  "prompt": "How many rounds of admission will be conducted for an MBA at NIT Trichy?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge up to October 2023, the **National Institute of Technology (NIT) Trichy** primarily focuses on engineering, technology, and related disciplines. NIT Trichy offers undergraduate, postgraduate, and doctoral programs in various engineering and science fields. However, it does **not offer a traditional Master of Business Administration (MBA) program**.\n\nIf you're interested in pursuing management studies in India, you might consider other prestigious institutions that specialize in MBA programs, such as the Indian Institutes of Management (IIMs), XLRI Xavier School of Management, or other reputable business schools.\n\n**Recommendations:**\n\n1. **Verify Official Sources:** Always check the [official NIT Trichy website](https://www.nitt.edu/home/) or contact their admissions office directly for the most accurate and up-to-date information regarding available programs.\n\n2. **Explore Alternative Programs:** If you're interested in management within a technical context, NIT Trichy does offer programs like M.Tech. in Industrial Engineering and Management, which combines engineering with management principles.\n\n3. **Consider Other Institutions for MBA:** If a traditional MBA is your goal, researching institutions specifically offering MBA programs would be beneficial. These schools typically have multiple admission rounds, including online applications, written tests, interviews, and group discussions.\n\nFeel free to provide more details or ask further questions if you need guidance on MBA programs or related fields!",
